name: Zehyn - The Assassin
description:
Jo and Layla Super Villain Series:
The Underworld used to call him The Assassin. A bounty hunter from Planet Vaiken. He currently lives in Cyber ​​Town, one of the largest space stations in the galaxy NGC 224.

Zehyn is famous for being cruel and merciless in eliminating his enemy. He has a past story with Layla and hates her very much after Layla was considered a traitor by joining the Vaiken secret agency unit.

Zehyn is the mastermind behind the events on Planet Vaiken, so now Jo and Layla are on the bounty hunter's list of targets.
